{"tid":1447191,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"[外國人快入]揸外國護照既人入嚟！！！！","createTime":"2019-08-11T15:40:29.000Z","updateTime":"2019-08-11T16:34:36.000Z","uid":133495,"like":4,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":4,"replies":[{"pid":"1c99e3cda29d3696c867ee6807c2d19a98c69bc2","tid":1447191,"uid":133495,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-11T15:40:29.000Z","msg":"我自己拎住西方國家護照，但<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">香港先係我屋企</span></span>。<br />\n我夠膽講我發夢次數，一定多過好多香港人。<br />\n既然有多一重身份就有多重責任，果本passport 唔係比你拍拍屎忽走！<br />\n相信你都係咁諗，先會仲係連登睇post<br />\n<br />\n諗諗呢個身份點樣可以做更多<br />\n<br />\n例如: 要求某國開放領事館。<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">大部份領事都係喺港島主戰線，如果可以開放絕對救到義士</span></span><br />\n<br />\n要求佢地派人保護國民。香港已經唔再安全，國家係有義務用一切辦法保護外國既國民。<br />\n<br />\n要求佢哋對香港進行製裁，例如旅遊警示、經濟製裁等<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">求集思廣益</span></span>"},{"pid":"b0b9e797817ebd9f520118a043f0b149483f0d33","tid":1447191,"uid":258192,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-11T15:42:13.000Z","msg":"有外國passport係咪比人捉都可以叫大使館幫手 其實佢地應該唔敢落charge"},{"pid":"2e10088db60fd0cb8f7b771e0dbc9ed1e5b47cbe","tid":1447191,"uid":133495,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"b0b9e797817ebd9f520118a043f0b149483f0d33","tid":1447191,"uid":258192,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-11T15:42:13.000Z","msg":"有外國passport係咪比人捉都可以叫大使館幫手 其實佢地應該唔敢落charge"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-11T15:49:24.000Z","msg":"如果現場捉斷正就未必<br />\n會唔會帶passport出街好？"},{"pid":"2cf63493be0051ecdd859619d51ab04bb5617544","tid":1447191,"uid":96704,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"2e10088db60fd0cb8f7b771e0dbc9ed1e5b47cbe","tid":1447191,"uid":133495,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"b0b9e797817ebd9f520118a043f0b149483f0d33","tid":1447191,"uid":258192,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-11T15:42:13.000Z","msg":"有外國passport係咪比人捉都可以叫大使館幫手 其實佢地應該唔敢落charg